# Spotify Web API — Client Credentials Flow
# Get these from https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard
#  1. Log in with your normal Spotify account (free or premium — both work)
#  2. Click "Create app" → name it anything, e.g. "Intents Planner"
#  3. Redirect URI: http://localhost:3000 (required field but unused for this flow)
#  4. Save → open the app → "Settings" → copy Client ID + Client secret
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in the values below.
# Without these, the app falls back to Spotify search URLs (still works, just less precise).

SPOTIFY_CLIENT_ID=
SPOTIFY_CLIENT_SECRET=
